38fed1e5174","tid":2335434,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:10:58.000Z","msg":"去過北歐 同 西伯利亞<br />\n<br />\n凍到仆街，你唔帶手套 唔止係feel到凍 ，皮膚係痛，落雪又麻煩 又污穢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港算好好"}]}